Berikut contoh penggunaan semua fitur utama API Anda menggunakan curl, dengan JWT token yang Anda berikan:

**Ganti data JSON sesuai kebutuhan.**

---

### 1. Register User
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"username":"user2","password":"pass"}'
```

### 2. Login User
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"username":"user1","password":"pass"}'
```

### 3. Get Profile (Butuh JWT)
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/auth/profile \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIxIiwic3ViIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NTgwNjQyNzUsImV4cCI6MTc1ODA2Nzg3NX0.WO9wFIo1UuqZCKRUFSQlNR6BKUVXZgUThooELcZ1Gqg"
```

---

## TODO (semua endpoint butuh JWT)

### 4. List Todo
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/todos \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIxIiwic3ViIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NTgwNjQyNzUsImV4cCI6MTc1ODA2Nzg3NX0.WO9wFIo1UuqZCKRUFSQlNR6BKUVXZgUThooELcZ1Gqg"
```

### 5. Create Todo
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/todos \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIxIiwic3ViIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NTgwNjQyNzUsImV4cCI6MTc1ODA2Nzg3NX0.WO9wFIo1UuqZCKRUFSQlNR6BKUVXZgUThooELcZ1Gqg" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"title":"Belajar NestJS","description":"Latihan membuat todo"}'
```

### 6. Get Todo by ID
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/todos/1 \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIxIiwic3ViIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NTgwNjQyNzUsImV4cCI6MTc1ODA2Nzg3NX0.WO9wFIo1UuqZCKRUFSQlNR6BKUVXZgUThooELcZ1Gqg"
```

### 7. Update Todo
```bash
curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3000/todos/1 \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIxIiwic3ViIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NTgwNjQyNzUsImV4cCI6MTc1ODA2Nzg3NX0.WO9wFIo1UuqZCKRUFSQlNR6BKUVXZgUThooELcZ1Gqg" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"title":"Update Judul"}'
```

### 8. Delete Todo
```bash
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:3000/todos/1 \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIxIiwic3ViIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NTgwNjQyNzUsImV4cCI6MTc1ODA2Nzg3NX0.WO9wFIo1UuqZCKRUFSQlNR6BKUVXZgUThooELcZ1Gqg"
```

---

## ARTICLE (semua endpoint butuh JWT)

> NOTE: The `articles` endpoints in this example require both a valid JWT (Authorization Bearer) and an API key header `X-API-KEY`.
> Set a demo key via the `API_KEYS` environment variable (comma-separated). Default in this project: `my-demo-api-key`.

### 9. List Article
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/articles \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIxIiwic3ViIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NTgwNjQyNzUsImV4cCI6MTc1ODA2Nzg3NX0.WO9wFIo1UuqZCKRUFSQlNR6BKUVXZgUThooELcZ1Gqg" \
  -H "X-API-KEY: my-demo-api-key"
```

### 10. Create Article
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/articles \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIxIiwic3ViIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NTgwNjQyNzUsImV4cCI6MTc1ODA2Nzg3NX0.WO9wFIo1UuqZCKRUFSQlNR6BKUVXZgUThooELcZ1Gqg" \
  -H "X-API-KEY: my-demo-api-key" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"title":"Judul Artikel","content":"Isi artikel"}'
```

### 11. Get Article by ID
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/articles/1 \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIxIiwic3ViIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NTgwNjQyNzUsImV4cCI6MTc1ODA2Nzg3NX0.WO9wFIo1UuqZCKRUFSQlNR6BKUVXZgUThooELcZ1Gqg" \
  -H "X-API-KEY: my-demo-api-key"
```

### 12. Update Article
```bash
curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3000/articles/1 \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIxIiwic3ViIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NTgwNjQyNzUsImV4cCI6MTc1ODA2Nzg3NX0.WO9wFIo1UuqZCKRUFSQlNR6BKUVXZgUThooELcZ1Gqg" \
  -H "X-API-KEY: my-demo-api-key" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"title":"Update Judul Artikel"}'
```

### 13. Delete Article
```bash
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:3000/articles/1 \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIxIiwic3ViIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NTgwNjQyNzUsImV4cCI6MTc1ODA2Nzg3NX0.WO9wFIo1UuqZCKRUFSQlNR6BKUVXZgUThooELcZ1Gqg" \
  -H "X-API-KEY: my-demo-api-key"
```

---

Jika ada endpoint lain yang ingin dicontohkan, silakan sebutkan!